Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}總會有一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飄落下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}屬於我的藍色天使啊{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:29.26,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}啊　那擦肩而過的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:34.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}彎下身去發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:41.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}轉身去呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}現在的內心裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:52.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就像雪一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}堆積起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:59.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}純真的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:04.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就算繞了些遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:07.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:12.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}也想直接親口告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:15.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}總會有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飛向藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:24.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}屬於我的藍色天使啊{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつからか
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.75,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}舞い降りた
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.78,0:01:29.26,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}Ah　すれ違う微笑みに
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.13,0:01:34.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}うつむくしかできずに
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.30,0:01:41.13,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}背中ごしに声かけたの
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.31,0:01:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}今は心の中で
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.56,0:01:52.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}それは雪のように
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}降りつもった
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.09,0:01:59.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}イノセントな痛み
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.73,0:02:04.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}たとえ遠まわりでも
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.76,0:02:07.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}この想いは
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.43,0:02:12.44,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}まっすぐ届けたい
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.18,0:02:15.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつの日か
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飛びたってゆけ
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.42,0:02:24.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
